2 implicitly by its real and imaginary parts of type unsigned long int.

22#include "mpc-impl.h"
23
24int
25mpc_ui_ui_sub (mpc_ptr rop, unsigned long int re, unsigned long int im,
26 mpc_srcptr op, mpc_rnd_t rnd)
27{
28 int inex_re, inex_im;
29
30 inex_re = mpfr_ui_sub (mpc_realref (rop), re, mpc_realref (op), MPC_RND_RE (rnd));
31 inex_im = mpfr_ui_sub (mpc_imagref (rop), im, mpc_imagref (op), MPC_RND_IM (rnd));
32
33 return MPC_INEX (inex_re, inex_im);
34}
